1
00:00:25,734 --> 00:00:27,528
INTERESTING.

2
00:00:27,653 --> 00:00:28,863
AN ARKTURIAN MACBETH.

3
00:00:28,988 --> 00:00:31,323
WATCH HIM.

4
00:00:31,448 --> 00:00:32,825
WATCH MACBETH.

5
00:00:53,052 --> 00:00:54,889
IS HE DEAD?

6
00:00:55,014 --> 00:00:58,809
SPEAK.
IS KING DUNCAN DEAD?

7
00:00:58,934 --> 00:01:02,437
ALL GREAT NEPTUNE'S
OCEAN,

8
00:01:02,563 --> 00:01:07,317
WASH THIS BLOOD
CLEAN FROM MY HANDS.

9
00:01:07,442 --> 00:01:09,904
THAT VOICE.

10
00:01:10,029 --> 00:01:12,197
HOW IS IT WITH ME, WHEN
EVERY NOISE APPALLS ME?

11
00:01:12,322 --> 00:01:15,492
THAT MAN
ON THE STAGE.

12
00:01:15,617 --> 00:01:17,912
I'M CERTAIN OF IT.

13
00:01:18,037 --> 00:01:20,414
THAT'S KODOS...

14
00:01:20,539 --> 00:01:22,165
THE EXECUTIONER.

15
00:01:22,290 --> 00:01:25,377
PLUCK'D OUT MINE EYES!

16
00:01:32,426 --> 00:01:36,722
Kirk: SPACE--THE FINAL FRONTIER.

17
00:01:36,847 --> 00:01:40,059
THESE ARE THE VOYAGES OF
THE STARSHIP "ENTERPRISE."

18
00:01:40,183 --> 00:01:41,936
ITS 5-YEAR MISSION--

19
00:01:42,061 --> 00:01:45,814
TO EXPLORE
STRANGE NEW WORLDS...

20
00:01:45,940 --> 00:01:48,901
TO SEEK OUT NEW LIFE
AND NEW CIVILIZATIONS...

21
00:01:49,026 --> 00:01:53,113
TO BOLDLY GO WHERE NO MAN
HAS GONE BEFORE.

22
00:02:26,730 --> 00:02:30,985
Kirk: CAPTAIN'S LOG--
STARDATE 2817.6.

23
00:02:31,110 --> 00:02:33,862
STARSHIP "ENTERPRISE" DIVERTED
FROM SCHEDULED COURSE.

24
00:02:33,988 --> 00:02:37,866
PURPOSE--TO CONFIRM DISCOVERY
BY DR. THOMAS LEIGHTON

25
00:02:37,992 --> 00:02:40,077
OF AN EXTRAORDINARY
NEW SYNTHETIC FOOD

26
00:02:40,201 --> 00:02:42,663
WHICH WOULD TOTALLY END
THE THREAT OF FAMINE

27
00:02:42,788 --> 00:02:45,916
ON SIGNIA MINOR,
A NEARBY EARTH COLONY.

28
00:02:47,375 --> 00:02:50,754
YOU MEAN TO TELL ME YOU'VE
CALLED ME 3 LIGHT-YEARS
OFF MY COURSE

29
00:02:50,879 --> 00:02:53,799
JUST TO ACCUSE AN ACTOR
OF BEING KODOS?

30
00:02:53,924 --> 00:02:57,761
HE IS KODOS.
I'M SURE OF IT.

31
00:02:57,886 --> 00:03:00,305
YOU SAID YOU DISCOVERED
A NEW FOOD CONCENTRATE.

32
00:03:00,430 --> 00:03:01,556
WHAT AM I SUPPOSED
TO PUT IN MY LOG,

33
00:03:01,682 --> 00:03:03,308
THAT YOU LIED, THAT YOU
DIVERTED A STARSHIP

34
00:03:03,433 --> 00:03:05,435
WITH FALSE INFORMATION?

35
00:03:05,560 --> 00:03:06,394
YOU'RE NOT ONLY IN TROUBLE,

36
00:03:06,520 --> 00:03:08,271
YOU'VE PUT ME
IN TROUBLE, TOO.

37
00:03:08,396 --> 00:03:10,774
I DID IT
TO TRAP KODOS!

38
00:03:10,899 --> 00:03:12,818
KODOS...

39
00:03:12,943 --> 00:03:14,611
IS DEAD.

40
00:03:14,736 --> 00:03:16,404
IS HE?

41
00:03:16,530 --> 00:03:17,990
IS ANYONE SURE?

42
00:03:18,115 --> 00:03:20,784
A BODY BURNED
BEYOND RECOGNITION?

43
00:03:20,909 --> 00:03:23,912
TOM,
THE AUTHORITIES CLOSED
THE BOOK ON THAT CASE

44
00:03:24,038 --> 00:03:25,164
YEARS AGO.

45
00:03:25,288 --> 00:03:27,124
THEN LET'S REOPEN IT.

46
00:03:27,248 --> 00:03:30,585
JIM, 4,000 PEOPLE
WERE BUTCHERED.

47
00:03:32,087 --> 00:03:33,047
MARTHA, WILL YOU
TELL HIM?

48
00:03:33,172 --> 00:03:35,256
I CAN'T TELL HIM
ANYTHING, JIM.

49
00:03:35,382 --> 00:03:36,299
HE'S BEEN LIKE THIS

50
00:03:36,424 --> 00:03:38,301
SINCE THE COMPANY
OF ACTORS ARRIVED.

51
00:03:42,723 --> 00:03:44,808
KODOS IS DEAD.

52
00:03:44,933 --> 00:03:46,018
I'M SATISFIED
WITH THAT.

53
00:03:46,143 --> 00:03:49,063
WELL, I'M NOT.

54
00:03:49,188 --> 00:03:51,106
I REMEMBER HIM.

55
00:03:52,399 --> 00:03:55,402
THAT VOICE.

56
00:03:55,527 --> 00:03:57,654
THE BLOODY THING HE DID.

57
00:04:01,950 --> 00:04:03,618
JIM...

58
00:04:03,744 --> 00:04:06,329
JIM, I NEED YOUR HELP.

59
00:04:06,454 --> 00:04:07,998
THERE WERE ONLY
8 OR 9 OF US

60
00:04:08,123 --> 00:04:10,417
WHO ACTUALLY SAW KODOS.

61
00:04:10,542 --> 00:04:12,920
I WAS ONE.
YOU'RE ANOTHER.

62
00:04:13,045 --> 00:04:14,213
IF HE'S TO BE EXPOSED--

63
00:04:14,337 --> 00:04:15,547
HE'S DEAD.

64
00:04:18,258 --> 00:04:19,551
THEN
IT WILL BE A GHOST

65
00:04:19,676 --> 00:04:23,722
MARTHA AND I RECEIVE
IN OUR HOME TONIGHT.

66
00:04:23,847 --> 00:04:25,306
I INVITED
THE ENTIRE COMPANY

67
00:04:25,432 --> 00:04:28,060
TO A COCKTAIL PARTY.

68
00:04:28,185 --> 00:04:30,187
I HAVE TO BE SURE.

69
00:04:30,311 --> 00:04:32,397
I HAVE TO GET
BACK TO MY SHIP

70
00:04:32,522 --> 00:04:33,273
AND FIGURE OUT
HOW I'M GONNA

71
00:04:33,398 --> 00:04:35,776
ENTER ALL THIS
IN MY LOG.

72
00:04:35,901 --> 00:04:37,485
TOM. MARTHA.

73
00:04:50,082 --> 00:04:52,251
Electronic voice:
LIBRARY COMPUTER.

74
00:04:52,375 --> 00:04:54,586
HISTORY FILES.

75
