ACTION.

311
00:16:54,388 --> 00:16:55,222
I DON'T WISH
TO DISCUSS IT,
MR. SPOCK.

312
00:16:55,348 --> 00:16:57,016
PLEASE FOLLOW
MY ORDERS.

313
00:16:59,101 --> 00:17:02,271
MR. SPOCK, WHEN
THE MAN ON TOP
WALKS ALONG HIS STREET,

314
00:17:02,396 --> 00:17:04,440
THE CHAIN OF COMMAND
IS OFTEN A NOOSE.

315
00:17:04,565 --> 00:17:06,985
SPARE ME
YOUR PHILOSOPHICAL
METAPHORS, DOCTOR.

316
00:17:09,236 --> 00:17:10,864
CAPTAIN IS
ACTING STRANGELY.

317
00:17:10,989 --> 00:17:13,199
I'M ASKING
IF YOU'VE NOTICED.

318
00:17:13,324 --> 00:17:15,535
NEGATIVE. YOU KNOW, THIS IS
THE FIRST TIME IN A WEEK

319
00:17:15,660 --> 00:17:18,496
THAT I'VE HAD TIME
FOR A DROP OF A DREW?

320
00:17:18,621 --> 00:17:20,665
WOULD YOU CARE
