321
00:17:20,790 --> 00:17:22,124
MY FATHER'S RACE
WAS SPARED

322
00:17:22,249 --> 00:17:24,919
THE DUBIOUS BENEFITS
OF ALCOHOL.

323
00:17:25,044 --> 00:17:27,547
OH. NOW I KNOW
WHY THEY WERE CONQUERED.

324
00:17:27,672 --> 00:17:29,215
WHAT ARE YOU SO
WORRIED ABOUT, ANYWAY?

325
00:17:29,340 --> 00:17:31,676
I FIND JIM
GENERALLY KNOWS
WHAT HE'S DOING.

326
00:17:31,801 --> 00:17:33,093
IT WAS ILLOGICAL
FOR HIM

327
00:17:33,219 --> 00:17:34,762
TO BRING THOSE
PLAYERS ABOARD.

328
00:17:34,888 --> 00:17:36,890
ILLOGICAL? DID YOU
GET A LOOK

329
00:17:37,015 --> 00:17:37,473
AT THAT
LITTLE JULIET?

330
00:17:37,598 --> 00:17:41,644
THAT'S A PRETTY
EXCITING CREATURE.

331
00:17:41,769 --> 00:17:44,188
OF COURSE, YOUR
PERSONAL CHEMISTRY

332
00:17:44,313 --> 00:17:47,274
WOULD PREVENT YOU
FROM SEEING THAT.

333
00:17:47,400 --> 00:17:48,275
DID IT EVER
OCCUR TO YOU

334
00:17:48,401 --> 00:17:50,528
THAT HE SIMPLY
MIGHT LIKE THE GIRL?

335
00:17:50,653 --> 00:17:53,614
IT OCCURRED.
I DISMISSED IT.

336
00:17:53,740 --> 00:17:55,616
YOU WOULD.

337
00:17:55,742 --> 00:17:56,868
DID YOU KNOW THAT HE
SUDDENLY TRANSFERRED

338
00:17:56,993 --> 00:17:58,870
LIEUTENANT RILEY
TO ENGINEERING?

339
00:17:58,995 --> 00:18:00,038
LOTS OF THINGS
ARE GOING AROUND HERE

340
00:18:00,162 --> 00:18:02,040
THAT I DON'T KNOW,
MR. SPOCK.

341
00:18:02,164 --> 00:18:04,250
NOW, HE'S THE CAPTAIN.
HE CAN TRANSFER PEOPLE
AS HE PLEASES.

342
00:18:04,375 --> 00:18:05,626
YOU CAN LOOK THAT UP
IN 100 VOLUMES

343
00:18:05,752 --> 00:18:07,754
OF SPACE REGULATIONS
SOMEWHERE,
ALL RIGHT?

344
00:18:07,879 --> 00:18:09,338
ALL RIGHT.
NOW, COME ON.
HAVE A DRINK.

345
00:18:09,463 --> 00:18:11,799
NO, THANK YOU.

346
00:18:11,925 --> 00:18:14,093
WELL,
YOU'RE WELCOME,
BUT I WILL,

347
00:18:14,218 --> 00:18:15,803
AND PLEASE,
MR. SPOCK,

348
00:18:15,929 --> 00:18:18,097
IF YOU WON'T
JOIN ME,

349
00:18:18,222 --> 00:18:20,140
DON'T DISAPPROVE
OF ME,

350
00:18:20,266 --> 00:18:22,476
AT LEAST NOT UNTIL
YOU'VE TRIED IT,
HUH?

351
00:18:24,896 --> 00:18:26,439
[SIGH]

352
00:18:31,444 --> 00:18:33,404
THIS IS THE, UH,
OBSERVATION DECK.

353
00:18:33,529 --> 00:18:35,239
THAT'S THE FLIGHT
DECK DOWN THERE--

354
00:18:35,364 --> 00:18:38,034
WITH
THE SHUTTLE CRAFT.

355
00:18:38,158 --> 00:18:39,077
INTERESTING.

356
00:18:39,201 --> 00:18:40,995
ISN'T IT?

357
00:18:41,120 --> 00:18:42,413
TELL ME,
CAPTAIN KIRK.

358
00:18:42,538 --> 00:18:43,289
ANYTHING.

359
00:18:43,414 --> 00:18:44,874
DID YOU ORDER
THE SOFT LIGHTS

360
00:18:44,999 --> 00:18:46,667
ESPECIALLY
FOR THE OCCASION?

361
00:18:48,836 --> 00:18:52,632
IF I HAD ORDERED
SOFT LIGHTS,

362
00:18:52,757 --> 00:18:55,802
I'D ALSO HAVE ARRANGED
FOR MUSIC AND FLOWERS.

363
00:18:56,886 --> 00:18:58,387
UNFORTUNATELY,
IT ISN'T SO.

364
00:18:58,512 --> 00:18:59,931
ON THE "ENTERPRISE,"
WE TRY TO DUPLICATE

365
00:19:00,056 --> 00:19:01,975
EARTH CONDITIONS
OF NIGHT AND DAY

366
00:19:02,100 --> 00:19:04,268
AS CLOSELY AS POSSIBLE.

367
00:19:04,393 --> 00:19:08,022
STAR LIGHT, STAR BRIGHT.

368
00:19:08,188 --> 00:19:10,316
I WISH I MAY,
I WISH I MIGHT.

369
00:19:10,441 --> 00:19:12,234
DO YOU REMEMBER THAT,
CAPTAIN?

370
00:19:12,359 --> 00:19:13,820
IT'S VERY OLD.

371
00:19:13,945 --> 00:19:16,114
ALMOST AS OLD
AS THE STARS THEMSELVES.

372
00:19:17,824 --> 00:19:20,034
AND THIS SHIP.

373
00:19:20,159 --> 00:19:23,203
ALL THIS POWER
SURGING AND THROBBING,

374
00:19:23,329 --> 00:19:24,538
YET UNDER CONTROL.

375
00:19:26,499 --> 00:19:28,584
ARE YOU LIKE THAT, CAPTAIN?

376
00:19:37,259 --> 00:19:41,097
ALL THIS POWER
AT YOUR COMMAND,

377
00:19:41,221 --> 00:19:42,849
THE DECISIONS
THAT YOU HAVE TO MAKE...

378
00:19:42,974 --> 00:19:45,601
COME FROM A VERY
HUMAN SOURCE.

379
00:19:45,726 --> 00:19:47,478
ARE YOU, CAPTAIN?

380
00:19:47,603 --> 00:19:48,938
HUMAN?

381
00:19:51,357 --> 00:19:52,775
YOU CAN COUNT ON IT.

382
00:19:52,900 --> 00:19:55,486
TELL ME ABOUT THE WOMEN
IN YOUR WORLD, CAPTAIN.

383
00:19:56,362 --> 00:19:58,072
I'D RATHER
TALK ABOUT YOU.

384
00:19:59,323 --> 00:20:00,616
YOU MUST HAVE
WANTED TO PERFORM

385
00:20:00,741 --> 00:20:02,910
SINCE THE FIRST TIME
YOU SAW YOUR FATHER ACT.

386
00:20:03,036 --> 00:20:04,453
WHEN WAS THAT?

387
00:20:04,578 --> 00:20:05,663
IN THE BEGINNING.

388
00:20:05,788 --> 00:20:06,539
TELL ME ABOUT THAT.

389
00:20:06,664 --> 00:20:08,124
THAT'S NOT FAIR.

390
00:20:08,248 --> 00:20:10,334
YOU HAVEN'T ANSWERED
MY QUESTION.

391
00:20:10,459 --> 00:20:11,711
ABOUT THE WOMEN.

392
00:20:11,836 --> 00:20:13,963
WHAT WOULD YOU
LIKE TO KNOW?

393
00:20:14,088 --> 00:20:16,174
HAS THE MACHINE
CHANGED THEM?

394
00:20:16,298 --> 00:20:19,719
MADE THEM JUST PEOPLE
INSTEAD OF WOMEN?

395
00:20:22,596 --> 00:20:24,473
WORLDS MAY CHANGE,

396
00:20:24,598 --> 00:20:25,933
GALAXIES DISINTEGRATE,

397
00:20:26,059 --> 00:20:28,519
BUT A WOMAN...

398
00:20:28,644 --> 00:20:30,938
ALWAYS REMAINS A WOMAN.

399
00:20:31,064 --> 00:20:32,982
ALL THIS...

400
00:20:33,107 --> 00:20:34,984
AND POWER, TOO.

401
00:20:36,318 --> 00:20:39,739
THE CAESAR
OF THE STARS

402
00:20:39,864 --> 00:20:42,408
AND THE CLEOPATRA
TO WORSHIP HIM.

