418
00:21:38,172 --> 00:21:40,007
ACCORDING TO
OUR LIBRARY BANKS,

419
00:21:40,133 --> 00:21:41,926
IT STARTED
ON THE EARTH COLONY
OF TARSUS IV

420
00:21:42,051 --> 00:21:43,469
WHEN THE FOOD SUPPLY
WAS ATTACKED

421
00:21:43,594 --> 00:21:45,805
BY AN EXOTIC FUNGUS
AND LARGELY
DESTROYED.

422
00:21:45,930 --> 00:21:47,140
THERE WERE
OVER 8,000 COLONISTS

423
00:21:47,265 --> 00:21:49,183
AND VIRTUALLY
NO FOOD.

424
00:21:49,308 --> 00:21:51,644
AND THAT WAS WHEN
GOVERNOR KODOS
SEIZED FULL POWER

425
00:21:51,769 --> 00:21:53,104
AND DECLARED
EMERGENCY
MARTIAL LAW.

426
00:21:53,229 --> 00:21:54,688
I'VE HEARD OF IT.

427
00:21:54,814 --> 00:21:55,606
YOU MAY NOT HAVE
HEARD IT ALL.

428
00:21:55,731 --> 00:21:58,400
KODOS BEGAN
TO SEPARATE
THE COLONISTS.

429
00:21:58,525 --> 00:21:59,526
SOME WOULD LIVE,

430
00:21:59,652 --> 00:22:01,988
BE RATIONED WHATEVER
FOOD WAS LEFT.

431
00:22:02,113 --> 00:22:05,116
THE REMAINDER
WOULD BE IMMEDIATELY
PUT TO DEATH.

432
00:22:05,241 --> 00:22:08,368
APPARENTLY, HE HAD
HIS OWN THEORIES
OF EUGENICS.

433
00:22:08,494 --> 00:22:10,997
UNFORTUNATELY,
HE WASN'T THE FIRST.

434
00:22:11,122 --> 00:22:12,665
PERHAPS NOT,
BUT HE WAS CERTAINLY

435
00:22:12,790 --> 00:22:15,626
AMONG THE MOST RUTHLESS
TO DECIDE ARBITRARILY

436
00:22:15,751 --> 00:22:16,376
WHO WOULD SURVIVE
AND WHO WOULD NOT,

437
00:22:16,502 --> 00:22:18,921
USING HIS OWN
PERSONAL STANDARDS

438
00:22:19,046 --> 00:22:21,174
AND THEN TO IMPLEMENT
HIS DECISION
WITHOUT MERCY.

439
00:22:21,299 --> 00:22:22,800
CHILDREN WATCHING
THEIR PARENTS DIE.

440
00:22:22,925 --> 00:22:24,384
WHOLE FAMILIES DESTROYED.

441
00:22:24,510 --> 00:22:26,386
OVER 4,000 PEOPLE.

442
00:22:26,512 --> 00:22:30,891
THEY DIED QUICKLY,
WITHOUT PAIN,
BUT THEY DIED.

443
00:22:31,017 --> 00:22:34,061
RELIEF ARRIVED,
BUT TOO LATE TO PREVENT
THE EXECUTIONS.

444
00:22:34,187 --> 00:22:35,562
AND KODOS,

445
00:22:35,688 --> 00:22:38,816
THERE NEVER WAS A POSITIVE
IDENTIFICATION OF HIS BODY.

446
00:22:38,941 --> 00:22:40,776
BUT WHAT IS
KARIDIAN TO DO
WITH IT?

447
00:22:40,901 --> 00:22:42,528
HIS HISTORY BEGINS

448
00:22:42,653 --> 00:22:46,615
ALMOST TO THE DAY
WHERE KODOS DISAPPEARED.

449
00:22:46,740 --> 00:22:49,618
AND YOU THINK JIM
SUSPECTS HE'S KODOS?

450
00:22:49,743 --> 00:22:51,912
HE'D BETTER.

451
00:22:52,038 --> 00:22:53,539
THERE WERE
9 EYEWITNESSES

452
00:22:53,664 --> 00:22:54,748
WHO SURVIVED
THE MASSACRE

453
00:22:54,874 --> 00:22:57,168
WHO'D ACTUALLY SEEN KODOS
WITH THEIR OWN EYES.

454
00:22:57,293 --> 00:22:59,753
JIM KIRK
WAS ONE OF THEM.

455
00:22:59,879 --> 00:23:02,340
WITH THE EXCEPTION
OF RILEY AND CAPTAIN KIRK,

456
00:23:02,464 --> 00:23:04,300
EVERY OTHER EYEWITNESS
IS DEAD,

457
00:23:04,424 --> 00:23:06,677
AND MY LIBRARY COMPUTER
SHOWS

458
00:23:06,802 --> 00:23:08,012
THAT WHEREVER THEY WERE--

459
00:23:08,137 --> 00:23:11,473
ON EARTH, ON A COLONY,
OR ABOARD SHIP--

460
00:23:11,598 --> 00:23:14,018
THE KARIDIAN
COMPANY OF PLAYERS
WAS SOMEWHERE NEAR

461
00:23:14,143 --> 00:23:15,895
WHEN THEY DIED.

462
00:23:17,146 --> 00:23:18,522
IT'S UNBELIEVABLE.

463
00:23:28,866 --> 00:23:32,661
HEY. REC ROOM. SOMEBODY.
TALK TO ME.

464
00:23:35,164 --> 00:23:36,832
LARRY MATSON
HERE.

465
00:23:36,957 --> 00:23:37,750
IS THAT YOU,
RILEY?

466
00:23:37,875 --> 00:23:38,918
WHAT'S UP?

467
00:23:39,043 --> 00:23:40,753
NOT ME.

468
00:23:40,878 --> 00:23:42,922
I AM DOWN.

469
00:23:43,047 --> 00:23:45,132
IN THE ENGINEERING ROOM.

470
00:23:45,258 --> 00:23:47,218
YOU'VE BEEN
A BAD BOY.

471
00:23:47,343 --> 00:23:49,053
MAYBE SO.

472
00:23:49,178 --> 00:23:50,096
WHATEVER I'VE DONE,
THEY'RE SURE KEEPING IT

473
00:23:50,221 --> 00:23:52,265
A SECRET FROM ME.

474
00:23:52,390 --> 00:23:54,725
HEY. IS THAT
UHURA PLAYING?

475
00:23:54,850 --> 00:23:56,352
LET ME TALK TO HER.

476
00:23:56,476 --> 00:23:57,853
I THINK
HIS HEART IS SORE.

477
00:23:59,521 --> 00:24:01,982
WHAT CAN I DO
FOR YOU, RILEY?

