00:24:02,108 --> 00:24:04,193
A SONG.

479
00:24:04,318 --> 00:24:06,320
YEP, MAKE IT
A LOVE SONG.

480
00:24:06,444 --> 00:24:09,447
JUST SOMETHING
TO REASSURE ME

481
00:24:09,573 --> 00:24:10,824
I'M NOT THE ONLY
LIVING THING

482
00:24:10,950 --> 00:24:13,077
LEFT IN
THE UNIVERSE, HUH?

483
00:24:13,202 --> 00:24:14,703
WELL, YOU'RE NOT.

484
00:24:14,828 --> 00:24:16,122
I'LL PROVE IT TO YOU.

485
00:24:22,753 --> 00:24:27,216
