497
00:25:42,208 --> 00:25:45,794
♪ WHERE MY
HEART IS ♪

498
00:25:45,919 --> 00:25:50,924
♪ WHERE MY LOVE
ETERNAL IS ♪

499
00:25:51,050 --> 00:25:53,469
♪ WAITING ♪

500
00:25:53,593 --> 00:25:57,181
♪ SOMEWHERE ♪

501
00:25:57,306 --> 00:26:02,144
♪ BEYOND THE STARS ♪

502
00:26:02,269 --> 00:26:15,157
♪ BEYOND ANTARES ♪

503
00:26:21,080 --> 00:26:23,082
HOW'D YOU LIKE THAT,
RILEY?

504
00:26:23,207 --> 00:26:24,291
[GAGS]

505
00:26:25,209 --> 00:26:26,085
[GAGS]

506
00:26:26,210 --> 00:26:28,795
[COUGHS]

507
00:26:28,921 --> 00:26:29,880
HELP ME...

508
00:26:30,005 --> 00:26:31,589
PLEASE.

509
00:26:33,842 --> 00:26:34,592
[GLASS SHATTERS]

510
00:26:43,018 --> 00:26:46,188
YOU'VE GOT TO
PULL HIM THROUGH.

511
00:26:46,313 --> 00:26:48,232
I'M NOT SURE I CAN.

512
00:26:48,357 --> 00:26:49,942
IF HE DIES,

513
00:26:50,067 --> 00:26:52,027
THE ONLY ONE
WHO'LL BE ABLE
TO IDENTIFY KODOS

514
00:26:52,152 --> 00:26:53,737
IS THE CAPTAIN,

515
00:26:53,862 --> 00:26:55,489
AND HE'LL BE
THE NEXT TARGET.

516
00:27:00,160 --> 00:27:03,247
Kirk: CAPTAIN'S LOG--
STARDATE 2819.1.

517
00:27:03,372 --> 00:27:05,374
SHIP'S OFFICER RILEY'S
CONDITION WORSENING.

518
00:27:05,499 --> 00:27:07,376
DR. McCOY MAKING LAB ANALYSIS

519
00:27:07,501 --> 00:27:10,087
TO DETERMINE CAUSE AND ANTIDOTE.

520
00:27:10,212 --> 00:27:12,381
ENTIRE CREW DEEPLY CONCERNED.

521
00:27:16,427 --> 00:27:18,178
AS OF THIS DATE,
LAB REPORT INDICATES

522
00:27:18,304 --> 00:27:19,054
PRESENCE OF
APPRECIABLE AMOUNT

523
00:27:19,179 --> 00:27:20,931
OF TETRALUBISOL,

524
00:27:21,056 --> 00:27:22,433
A HIGHLY
VOLATILE LUBRICANT

525
00:27:22,558 --> 00:27:23,601
IN USE ABOARD SHIP.

526
00:27:23,725 --> 00:27:25,936
SOMEONE TRIED
TO POISON HIM.

527
00:27:26,061 --> 00:27:28,063
TETRALUBISOL IS
A MILKY SUBSTANCE.

528
00:27:28,188 --> 00:27:29,607
SOMEONE COULD'VE
GOTTEN CARELESS
AND MADE A MISTAKE.

529
00:27:29,773 --> 00:27:31,484
I DON'T BELIEVE THAT
AND NEITHER DO YOU.

530
00:27:31,609 --> 00:27:33,444
I WANT THE CAPTAIN
TO SEE THAT REPORT.

531
00:27:33,569 --> 00:27:34,903
WHEN I'VE FINISHED
LOGGING IT.

532
00:27:35,028 --> 00:27:36,113
NOW.

533
00:27:38,365 --> 00:27:39,450
ALL RIGHT.

534
00:27:45,914 --> 00:27:47,541
[BUZZ]

535
00:27:47,665 --> 00:27:49,001
COME.

536
00:27:54,840 --> 00:27:56,467
MY REPORT
ON LIEUTENANT RILEY.

537
00:27:56,592 --> 00:27:57,593
WILL HE MAKE IT?

538
00:27:57,717 --> 00:27:59,428
HE'S GOT
A GOOD CHANCE.

539
00:27:59,553 --> 00:28:01,972
AND WE PREDICT
THE SAME
FOR YOU, CAPTAIN.

540
00:28:02,097 --> 00:28:05,100
ALL RIGHT,
MR. SPOCK.
LET'S HAVE IT.

541
00:28:05,225 --> 00:28:07,561
LIEUTENANT RILEY
WAS A WITNESS.

542
00:28:07,685 --> 00:28:09,021
SO WERE YOU.

543
00:28:10,481 --> 00:28:12,316
[SIGHS]

544
00:28:12,441 --> 00:28:13,567
ALL RIGHT.

545
00:28:13,691 --> 00:28:15,110
SOMEONE TRIED
TO KILL HIM.

546
00:28:15,235 --> 00:28:16,654
COULD HAVE BEEN
AN ACCIDENT.

547
00:28:16,778 --> 00:28:17,779
YOU SHOULD
BE TOLD THE DIFFERENCE

548
00:28:17,904 --> 00:28:21,408
BETWEEN EMPIRICISM
AND STUBBORNNESS,
DOCTOR.

549
00:28:21,534 --> 00:28:24,077
I CHECKED WITH
THE LIBRARY COMPUTER
JUST AS YOU DID.

550
00:28:24,203 --> 00:28:25,871
I GOT THE SAME
INFORMATION.

551
00:28:25,996 --> 00:28:27,080
AREN'T YOU GETTING
A LITTLE OUT OF LINE,
MR. SPOCK?

552
00:28:27,206 --> 00:28:28,748
MY PERSONAL BUSINESS--

553
00:28:28,874 --> 00:28:30,792
IT'S MY PERSONAL BUSINESS
WHEN IT MIGHT INTERFERE

554
00:28:30,917 --> 00:28:31,877
WITH THE SMOOTH OPERATION
OF THIS SHIP.

555
00:28:32,002 --> 00:28:32,919
YOU THINK
THAT HAPPENED?

556
00:28:33,045 --> 00:28:33,420
IT COULD HAPPEN.

557
00:28:33,546 --> 00:28:34,921
I DON'T LIKE
ANYONE MEDDLING

558
00:28:35,047 --> 00:28:35,881
IN MY PRIVATE AFFAIRS,

559
00:28:36,006 --> 00:28:37,174
NOT EVEN
MY SECOND IN COMMAND.

560
00:28:37,299 --> 00:28:39,092
JIM, SPOCK'S
SIMPLY TRYING--

561
00:28:39,218 --> 00:28:40,719
I KNOW WHAT HE'S TRYING
TO DO AND I DON'T
LIKE IT.

562
00:28:40,844 --> 00:28:42,596
IT'S HIS JOB
AND YOU KNOW IT.

563
00:28:47,226 --> 00:28:49,520
AND YOU ALSO KNOW...

564
00:28:49,645 --> 00:28:51,271
THAT NOTHING IS PROVEN.

565
00:28:51,397 --> 00:28:52,898
EVEN IN THIS CORNER
OF THE GALAXY, CAPTAIN,

566
00:28:53,023 --> 00:28:54,900
TWO PLUS TWO
EQUALS 4.

567
00:28:55,025 --> 00:28:57,819
ALMOST CERTAINLY AN ATTEMPT
WILL BE MADE TO KILL YOU.

568
00:28:57,944 --> 00:28:59,363
WHY DO YOU
INVITE DEATH?

569
00:28:59,488 --> 00:29:01,740
I'M NOT.

570
00:29:01,865 --> 00:29:03,325
I'M INTERESTED
IN JUSTICE.

571
00:29:03,950 --> 00:29:05,827
ARE YOU?

572
00:29:05,952 --> 00:29:07,829
ARE YOU SURE
IT'S NOT VENGEANCE?

573
00:29:09,206 --> 00:29:11,041
NO, I'M NOT SURE.

574
00:29:12,876 --> 00:29:14,086
I WISH I WAS.

575
00:29:16,755 --> 00:29:18,048
I'VE DONE THINGS
I'VE NEVER DONE BEFORE.

576
00:29:18,173 --> 00:29:20,342
I'VE PLACED MY COMMAND
IN JEOPARDY.

577
00:29:20,467 --> 00:29:21,510
FROM HERE ON,
I'VE GOT TO DETERMINE

578
00:29:21,635 --> 00:29:24,763
WHETHER OR NOT
KARIDIAN IS KODOS.

579
00:29:24,888 --> 00:29:27,516
HE IS.

580
00:29:27,641 --> 00:29:32,646
YOU SOUND CERTAIN.
I WISH I COULD BE.

581
00:29:32,771 --> 00:29:35,441
BEFORE I ACCUSE A MAN OF
THAT, I'VE GOT TO BE.

582
00:29:35,566 --> 00:29:38,860
I SAW HIM ONCE,
20 YEARS AGO.

583
00:29:38,985 --> 00:29:41,154
MEN CHANGE.
MEMORY CHANGES.

584
00:29:41,280 --> 00:29:42,489
LOOK AT HIM NOW--
HE'S AN ACTOR.

585
00:29:42,615 --> 00:29:44,450
HE'LL CHANGE
HIS APPEARANCE.

586
00:29:44,575 --> 00:29:49,455
NO. LOGIC IS NOT ENOUGH.

587
00:29:49,580 --> 00:29:52,165
I'VE GOT TO FEEL MY WAY.

588
00:29:52,291 --> 00:29:55,043
MAKE ABSOLUTELY SURE.

589
00:29:55,168 --> 00:29:57,713
WHAT IF YOU DECIDE
HE IS KODOS?
WHAT THEN?

590
00:29:57,837 --> 00:29:59,131
DO YOU PLAY GOD,

591
00:29:59,256 --> 00:30:01,592
CARRY HIS HEAD
THROUGH THE CORRIDORS
IN TRIUMPH?

592
00:30:01,717 --> 00:30:03,594
THAT WON'T
BRING BACK
THE DEAD, JIM.

593
00:30:05,512 --> 00:30:06,805
NO.

594
00:30:08,766 --> 00:30:10,392
BUT THEY MAY
REST EASIER.

595
00:30:15,897 --> 00:30:17,691
LOGIC, CAPTAIN.
DR. LEIGHTON
WAS MURDERED

596
00:30:17,816 --> 00:30:19,859
WHILE
THE KARIDIAN COMPANY
WAS ON PLANET Q.

597
00:30:19,985 --> 00:30:22,237
NOW AN ATTEMPT HAS
BEEN MADE AGAINST
LIEUTENANT RILEY

598
00:30:22,362 --> 00:30:23,863
WHILE THE COMPANY
IS ON BOARD
THE "ENTERPRISE."

599
00:30:23,989 --> 00:30:26,533
DOC ISN'T SURE THERE WAS
A MURDER ATTEMPT.

600
00:30:26,659 --> 00:30:27,785
BESIDES,
I HAVE AN IDEA
THAT MAY PROVE--

601
00:30:27,909 --> 00:30:29,328
SHH.
LISTEN.
[HUMMING ]

602
00:30:29,453 --> 00:30:31,913
DO YOU HEAR IT?
THAT LOW HUM.

603
00:30:32,038 --> 00:30:32,914
A PHASER.

604
00:30:33,039 --> 00:30:33,915
ON OVERLOAD.

605
00:30:34,040 --> 00:30:36,669
[HUMMING]

606
00:30:39,463 --> 00:30:40,964
THIS IS THE CAPTAIN.

607
00:30:41,089 --> 00:30:42,633
THERE'S A PHASER
ON OVERLOAD
IN MY QUARTERS.

608
00:30:42,758 --> 00:30:44,384
IF IT BLOWS,
IT'LL TAKE OUT
THE ENTIRE DECK.

609
00:30:44,510 --> 00:30:47,137
EVACUATE ALL PERSONNEL
IN THIS QUADRANT.

610
00:30:47,262 --> 00:30:48,806
DOUBLE RED ALERT.

611
00:30:48,930 --> 00:30:52,100
[SIREN]

612
00:30:52,225 --> 00:30:53,143
YOU GET OUT OF HERE.

613
00:30:53,268 --> 00:30:54,186
YOU CAN'T STAY.

614
00:30:54,311 --> 00:30:55,813
GO ON. BLOCK OFF
THIS SECTION.

615
00:30:55,937 --> 00:30:58,023
HURRY.
I'LL FIND IT.

616
00:30:58,148 --> 00:30:59,733
EVACUATE THIS SECTION.
SEAL IT OFF.

617
00:30:59,858 --> 00:31:01,901
CLEAR SECTION C4 AND C5.

618
00:31:37,062 --> 00:31:39,105
[EXPLOSION]

619
00:31:42,442 --> 00:31:43,527
[SIREN STOPS]

620
00:32:09,928 --> 00:32:10,637
[DOOR OPENS]

621
00:32:13,640 --> 00:32:16,560
WE'RE OVERDUE
FOR OUR TALK,
AREN'T WE?

622
00:32:16,685 --> 00:32:18,854
I HAD HOPED
YOU WOULD HAVE RESPECTED
MY PRIVACY, CAPTAIN.

623
00:32:18,978 --> 00:32:20,939
A MOMENT AGO,
WE NARROWLY AVERTED
AN EXPLOSION

624
00:32:21,064 --> 00:32:23,901
WHICH WOULD HAVE
DESTROYED SEVERAL DECKS
OF THIS SHIP.

625
00:32:24,025 --> 00:32:26,904
BEFORE THAT,
SOMEONE TRIED TO POISON
ONE OF MY CREWMEN.

626
00:32:27,028 --> 00:32:27,987
I AM SORRY
TO HEAR THAT.

627
00:32:28,113 --> 00:32:29,782
I'M SURE YOU ARE.

628
00:32:32,075 --> 00:32:33,243
ARE YOU KODOS?

629
00:32:37,664 --> 00:32:39,708
I ASKED YOU
A QUESTION.

630
00:32:39,833 --> 00:32:41,209
DO YOU BELIEVE
THAT I AM?

631
00:32:41,334 --> 00:32:43,211
I DO.

632
00:32:43,336 --> 00:32:45,380
THEN I AM KODOS,

633
00:32:45,505 --> 00:32:47,257
IF IT PLEASES YOU
TO BELIEVE SO.

634
00:32:49,008 --> 00:32:50,761
I AM AN ACTOR.

635
00:32:50,886 --> 00:32:52,178
I PLAY MANY PARTS.

636
00:32:52,304 --> 00:32:54,097
YOU'RE AN ACTOR NOW.

637
00:32:54,222 --> 00:32:55,808
WHAT WERE YOU
20 YEARS AGO?

638
00:32:58,351 --> 00:32:59,645
YOUNGER, CAPTAIN.

639
00:33:01,438 --> 00:33:02,648
MUCH YOUNGER.

640
00:33:03,774 --> 00:33:04,566
SO WAS I.

641
00:33:07,778 --> 00:33:08,654
BUT I REMEMBER.

642
00:33:13,241 --> 00:33:14,660
LET'S SEE IF YOU DO.

643
00:33:14,785 --> 00:33:17,579
READ THIS
INTO THAT COMMUNICATOR
ON THE WALL.

644
00:33:17,704 --> 00:33:19,706
IT WILL BE RECORDED

645
00:33:19,832 --> 00:33:23,585
AND COMPARED TO A PIECE
OF KODOS VOICE FILM
WE HAVE IN OUR FILES.

646
00:33:23,710 --> 00:33:25,295
THE TEST
IS VIRTUALLY INFALLIBLE.

647
00:33:25,420 --> 00:33:28,006
IT WILL TELL US WHETHER
YOU'RE KARIDIAN...

648
00:33:29,299 --> 00:33:31,217
OR KODOS
THE EXECUTIONER.

649
00:33:35,472 --> 00:33:37,724
READY FOR VOICE TEST.

650
00:33:37,850 --> 00:33:39,685
DISGUISING YOUR VOICE
WILL MAKE NO DIFFERENCE.

651
00:33:45,148 --> 00:33:47,066
"THE REVOLUTION...

652
00:33:47,192 --> 00:33:49,903
"IS SUCCESSFUL,

653
00:33:50,028 --> 00:33:53,114
"BUT SURVIVAL DEPENDS
ON DRASTIC MEASURES.

654
00:33:53,239 --> 00:33:54,533
"YOUR CONTINUED
EXISTENCE

655
00:33:54,658 --> 00:33:57,285
"REPRESENTS A THREAT
TO THE WELL-BEING
OF SOCIETY.

656
00:33:57,410 --> 00:34:00,413
"YOUR LIVES
MEANS SLOW DEATH

657
00:34:00,539 --> 00:34:02,165
"TO THE MORE
VALUED MEMBERS

658
00:34:02,290 --> 00:34:04,334
OF THE COLONY."

659
00:34:04,459 --> 00:34:06,003
THEREFORE
I HAVE NO ALTERNATIVE

660
00:34:06,127 --> 00:34:08,254
BUT TO SENTENCE YOU
TO DEATH.

661
00:34:08,380 --> 00:34:09,965
YOUR EXECUTION
IS SO ORDERED.

662
00:34:10,089 --> 00:34:11,758
SIGNED, KODOS,

663
00:34:11,884 --> 00:34:14,803
GOVERNOR OF TARSUS IV.

664
00:34:14,928 --> 00:34:16,304
I REMEMBER THE WORDS.

665
00:34:16,429 --> 00:34:17,514
I WROTE THEM DOWN.

666
00:34:19,892 --> 00:34:23,061
YOU SAID THEM
LIKE YOU KNEW THEM.

667
00:34:23,186 --> 00:34:25,313
YOU HARDLY GLANCED
AT THE PAPER.

668
00:34:25,438 --> 00:34:27,106
I LEARN MY PARTS
VERY QUICKLY.

669
00:34:27,232 --> 00:34:28,483
ARE YOU SURE?

670
00:34:28,608 --> 00:34:29,860
ARE YOU SURE YOU DIDN'T
ACT THIS ROLE OUT

671
00:34:29,985 --> 00:34:30,736
IN FRONT OF
A CAPTIVE AUDIENCE

672
00:34:30,861 --> 00:34:33,530
WHOM YOU BLASTED
OUT OF EXISTENCE
WITHOUT MERCY?

673
00:34:33,655 --> 00:34:36,700
I FIND YOUR USE
OF THE WORD "MERCY"

674
00:34:36,825 --> 00:34:38,577
STRANGELY INAPPROPRIATE,
CAPTAIN.

675
00:34:40,913 --> 00:34:43,373
HERE YOU STAND,
A PERFECT SYMBOL

676
00:34:43,498 --> 00:34:49,796
OF OUR TECHNICAL SOCIETY--
MECHANIZED, ELECTRONICIZED,

677
00:34:49,922 --> 00:34:51,172
AND NOT VERY HUMAN.

678
00:34:54,467 --> 00:34:56,636
YOU'VE DONE AWAY
WITH HUMANITY,

679
00:34:56,762 --> 00:34:59,848
THE STRIVING OF MAN
TO ACHIEVE GREATNESS

680
00:34:59,973 --> 00:35:02,100
THROUGH HIS OWN
RESOURCES.

681
00:35:02,225 --> 00:35:04,519
WE'VE ARMED MAN
WITH TOOLS.

682
00:35:04,644 --> 00:35:06,396
THE STRIVING
FOR GREATNESS CONTINUES.
BUT KODOS--

683
00:35:06,521 --> 00:35:09,066
KODOS, WHOEVER HE WAS--
OR IS.

684
00:35:09,232 --> 00:35:10,442
OR IS.

685
00:35:13,570 --> 00:35:16,531
KODOS MADE A DECISION
OF LIFE AND DEATH.

686
00:35:16,656 --> 00:35:19,534
SOME HAD TO DIE
THAT OTHERS MIGHT LIVE.

687
00:35:19,659 --> 00:35:20,827
YOU'RE A MAN OF DECISION,
CAPTAIN.

688
00:35:20,953 --> 00:35:22,079
YOU OUGHT TO
UNDERSTAND THAT.

689
00:35:22,203 --> 00:35:23,705
ALL I UNDERSTAND

690
00:35:23,830 --> 00:35:27,584
IS THAT 4,000 PEOPLE
WERE NEEDLESSLY
BUTCHERED.

691
00:35:27,709 --> 00:35:30,712
IN ORDER TO SAVE
4,000 OTHERS.

692
00:35:30,837 --> 00:35:31,463
AND IF THE SUPPLY SHIPS

693
00:35:31,588 --> 00:35:34,340
HADN'T COME EARLIER
THAN EXPECTED,

694
00:35:34,466 --> 00:35:36,051
THIS KODOS OF YOURS
MIGHT HAVE GONE DOWN
IN HISTORY

695
00:35:36,175 --> 00:35:37,010
AS A GREAT HERO.

696
00:35:37,135 --> 00:35:38,386
BUT HE DIDN'T.

697
00:35:38,511 --> 00:35:40,973
AND HISTORY
HAS MADE ITS JUDGMENT.

698
00:35:41,098 --> 00:35:43,767
IF YOU'RE SO SURE
THAT I'M KODOS,

699
00:35:43,892 --> 00:35:45,727
WHY NOT KILL ME NOW?

700
00:35:45,852 --> 00:35:49,815
LET BLOODY VENGEANCE
TAKE ITS FINAL COURSE!

701
00:35:49,940 --> 00:35:50,857
AND SEE
WHAT DIFFERENCE IT MAKES

702
00:35:50,983 --> 00:35:52,901
TO THIS UNIVERSE
OF YOURS.

703
00:35:53,026 --> 00:35:54,319
THOSE ARE
BEAUTIFUL WORDS,

704
00:35:54,444 --> 00:35:56,279
WELL ACTED.

705
00:35:56,404 --> 00:35:57,823
THEY CHANGE NOTHING.

706
00:35:57,948 --> 00:35:59,783
NO, I SUPPOSE NOT.

707
00:35:59,908 --> 00:36:01,618
THEY'RE MERELY TOOLS,

708
00:36:01,743 --> 00:36:02,953
LIKE THIS SHIP OF YOURS.

709
00:36:03,078 --> 00:36:04,830
THERE ARE NO
PREVIOUS RECORDS

710
00:36:04,955 --> 00:36:06,081
TO ANTON KARIDIAN

711
00:36:06,205 --> 00:36:07,874
PRIOR TO
20 YEARS AGO.

712
00:36:11,086 --> 00:36:12,378
BLOOD THINS.

713
00:36:13,296 --> 00:36:14,798
THE BODY FAILS.

714
00:36:16,133 --> 00:36:17,717
ONE IS FINALLY GRATEFUL

715
00:36:17,843 --> 00:36:19,427
FOR A FAILING MEMORY.

716
00:36:23,140 --> 00:36:25,058
I NO LONGER
TREASURE LIFE,

717
00:36:25,183 --> 00:36:26,643
NOT EVEN MY OWN.

718
00:36:29,521 --> 00:36:31,606
I AM TIRED!

719
00:36:36,277 --> 00:36:38,321
THE PAST...

720
00:36:38,446 --> 00:36:40,406
IS A BLANK.

721
00:36:45,411 --> 00:36:47,998
DID YOU GET
EVERYTHING YOU...

722
00:36:48,123 --> 00:36:50,416
WANTED,
CAPTAIN KIRK?

723
00:36:50,542 --> 00:36:51,751
IF I HAD GOTTEN...

724
00:36:54,337 --> 00:36:55,755
EVERYTHING I WANTED...

725
00:36:58,008 --> 00:37:00,218
YOU MIGHT NOT WALK
OUT OF THIS ROOM ALIVE.

726
00:37:02,595 --> 00:37:03,930
CAPTAIN KIRK.

727
00:37:08,351 --> 00:37:10,145
YOU BETTER REST...

728
00:37:10,269 --> 00:37:11,312
NOW.

729
00:37:18,862 --> 00:37:20,572
THERE'S
A STAIN OF CRUELTY

730
00:37:20,697 --> 00:37:23,324
ON YOUR
SHINING ARMOR,
CAPTAIN.

731
00:37:23,449 --> 00:37:25,827
YOU COULD HAVE
SPARED HIM...

732
00:37:25,952 --> 00:37:27,037
AND ME.

733
00:37:29,122 --> 00:37:31,666
YOU TALKED
OF USING TOOLS.

734
00:37:31,791 --> 00:37:33,418
I WAS A TOOL,
WASN'T I?

735
00:37:33,543 --> 00:37:36,462
A TOOL TO USE
AGAINST MY FATHER.

736
00:37:36,588 --> 00:37:37,756
IN THE BEGINNING,
PERHAPS.

737
00:37:39,758 --> 00:37:43,053
BUT LATER, I WANTED IT
TO BE MORE THAN THAT.

738
00:37:43,178 --> 00:37:46,890
LATER. EVERYTHING'S
ALWAYS LATER.

739
00:37:47,015 --> 00:37:52,145
LATER. LATEST.
TOO LATE.

740
00:37:52,270 --> 00:37:53,354
TOO LATE, CAPTAIN.

741
00:37:57,776 --> 00:37:59,861
YOU ARE
LIKE YOUR SHIP--

742
00:37:59,986 --> 00:38:01,821
POWERFUL...

743
00:38:01,947 --> 00:38:03,990
AND NOT HUMAN.

744
00:38:04,116 --> 00:38:06,743
THERE IS NO MERCY
IN YOU.

745
00:38:06,868 --> 00:38:09,454
IF HE IS KODOS,

746
00:38:09,579 --> 00:38:12,124
THEN I'VE SHOWN HIM
MORE MERCY THAN
HE DESERVES.

747
00:38:13,875 --> 00:38:15,043
AND IF HE ISN'T...

748
00:38:17,378 --> 00:38:19,089
THEN WE'LL
LET YOU OFF
AT BENECIA,

749
00:38:19,214 --> 00:38:21,091
AND NO HARM DONE.

750
00:38:24,469 --> 00:38:25,804
CAPTAIN KIRK.

751
00:38:27,055 --> 00:38:29,015
WHO ARE YOU TO SAY
WHAT HARM WAS DONE?

752
00:38:31,810 --> 00:38:33,103
WHO DO I HAVE TO BE?

753
00:38:38,066 --> 00:38:39,525
MEDICAL LOG--

754
00:38:39,651 --> 00:38:41,611
LIEUTENANT RILEY'S
SUFFICIENTLY RECOVERED

755
00:38:41,736 --> 00:38:42,487
TO BE DISCHARGED,

756
00:38:42,612 --> 00:38:43,863
BUT THE CAPTAIN
HAS ORDERED HIM

757
00:38:43,989 --> 00:38:45,406
RESTRICTED TO SICK BAY

758
00:38:45,531 --> 00:38:47,325
TO PREVENT
CONTACT WITH PASSENGER

759
00:38:47,450 --> 00:38:48,910
WHO CALLS HIMSELF
KARIDIAN

760
00:38:49,035 --> 00:38:52,538
AND WHO'S SUSPECTED
OF BEING KODOS
THE EXECUTIONER

761
00:38:52,664 --> 00:38:55,374
AND OF MURDERING
THE LIEUTENANT'S FAMILY.

762
00:39:05,635 --> 00:39:08,305
Kirk: CAPTAIN'S LOG--
STARDATE 2819.8.

763
00:39:08,429 --> 00:39:10,765
SUSPECT UNDER SURVEILLANCE.

764
00:39:10,890 --> 00:39:13,101
STRATEGIC AREAS
UNDER DOUBLE GUARD.

765
00:39:13,226 --> 00:39:14,227
PERFORMANCE OF
THE KARIDIAN PLAYERS

766
00:39:14,352 --> 00:39:16,229
TAKING PLACE AS SCHEDULED.

767
00:39:18,231 --> 00:39:20,900
[FANFARE PLAYS]

768
00:39:25,322 --> 00:39:26,114
TONIGHT, THE KARIDIAN PLAYERS

769
00:39:26,239 --> 00:39:27,991
PRESENT "HAMLET,"

770
00:39:28,116 --> 00:39:29,826
ANOTHER IN A SERIES
OF LIVING PLAYS

771
00:39:29,951 --> 00:39:31,369
PRESENTED IN SPACE,

772
00:39:31,494 --> 00:39:34,664
DEDICATED TO THE TRADITION
OF CLASSIC THEATER.

773
00:39:34,789 --> 00:39:36,166
"HAMLET" IS A VIOLENT PLAY

774
00:39:36,291 --> 00:39:38,668
ABOUT VIOLENT TIMES

775
00:39:38,793 --> 00:39:40,212
WHEN LIFE WAS CHEAP

776
00:39:40,337 --> 00:39:41,587
AND AMBITION WAS GOD.

777
00:39:49,137 --> 00:39:51,014
I BELIEVE
WE HAVE A MATCH,
CAPTAIN.

778
00:39:51,139 --> 00:39:53,850
BUT NOT
AN EXACT MATCH,
MR. SPOCK.

779
00:39:55,393 --> 00:39:58,730
WE'RE DEALING
WITH A MAN'S LIFE.

780
00:39:58,855 --> 00:40:01,274
NO MACHINE
CAN MAKE THAT DECISION.

781
00:40:01,440 --> 00:40:02,775
IN THE LONG HISTORY
OF MEDICINE,

782
00:40:02,901 --> 00:40:03,985
NO DOCTOR
HAS EVER CAUGHT

783
00:40:04,110 --> 00:40:05,320
THE FIRST FEW MINUTES
OF A PLAY.

784
00:40:05,444 --> 00:40:07,280
RILEY, DON'T
FORGET THAT--

785
00:40:10,742 --> 00:40:11,576
RILEY?

786
00:40:14,704 --> 00:40:16,998
CAPTAIN KIRK,
McCOY HERE.
Kirk: YES, DOCTOR.

787
00:40:17,123 --> 00:40:18,791
RILEY'S GONE.
I WAS RECORDING MY LOG

788
00:40:18,917 --> 00:40:20,001
ABOUT KARIDIAN AND KODOS.

789
00:40:20,126 --> 00:40:20,877
IF HE OVERHEARD--

790
00:40:21,002 --> 00:40:22,295
YOU'VE MADE YOUR POINT,
DOCTOR.

791
00:40:22,420 --> 00:40:25,298
CAPTAIN,
SECURITY, "H" DECK--

792
00:40:25,423 --> 00:40:27,550
THE WEAPONS LOCKER
HAS BEEN BROKEN INTO.

793
00:40:27,675 --> 00:40:29,844
ONE PHASER IS MISSING.

794
00:40:29,969 --> 00:40:31,054
THIS IS THE CAPTAIN.

795
00:40:31,179 --> 00:40:33,390
SECURITY 2 ALERT.

796
00:40:33,514 --> 00:40:35,350
FIND AND RESTRAIN
LIEUTENANT KEVIN RILEY.

797
00:40:35,474 --> 00:40:36,268
HE'S ARMED
AND POSSIBLY HEADED

798
00:40:36,393 --> 00:40:38,228
TOWARDS THE SHIP'S THEATER.

799
00:40:58,831 --> 00:41:00,208
WHITHER WILT THOU LEAD ME?

800
00:41:00,333 --> 00:41:02,627
SPEAK, I'LL GO NO FURTHER.

801
00:41:02,752 --> 00:41:04,754
MARK ME.

802
00:41:04,879 --> 00:41:06,214
Hamlet: I WILL.

803
00:41:06,339 --> 00:41:09,801
MY HOUR IS ALMOST COME,

804
00:41:09,926 --> 00:41:13,638
WHEN I TO SULPHUROUS
AND TORMENTING FIRES

805
00:41:13,763 --> 00:41:17,683
MUST RENDER UP MYSELF.

806
00:41:17,809 --> 00:41:20,228
Hamlet: SPEAK.
I AM BOUND TO HEAR.

807
00:41:20,353 --> 00:41:23,731
SO ART THOU
TO REVENGE...

808
00:41:24,816 --> 00:41:27,026
WHEN THOU SHALT HEAR.

809
00:41:27,152 --> 00:41:31,197
I AM THY FATHER'S
SPIRIT,

810
00:41:31,323 --> 00:41:32,949
DOOMED
FOR A CERTAIN TERM

811
00:41:33,074 --> 00:41:34,451
TO WALK THE NIGHT...

812
00:41:34,575 --> 00:41:36,619
RILEY...

813
00:41:36,744 --> 00:41:37,996
GET BACK
TO THE SICK BAY.

814
00:41:40,748 --> 00:41:43,251
HE MURDERED MY FATHER...

815
00:41:43,376 --> 00:41:45,128
AND MY MOTHER.

816
00:41:45,253 --> 00:41:47,255
YOU COULD BE WRONG.

817
00:41:47,380 --> 00:41:49,174
DON'T THROW AWAY
YOUR LIFE
ON A MISTAKE.

818
00:41:49,299 --> 00:41:51,343
I'M NOT WRONG.

819
00:41:51,468 --> 00:41:53,636
BUT THAT I AM FORBID
TO TELL THE SECRETS

820
00:41:53,761 --> 00:41:56,055
OF MY PRISON-HOUSE...

821
00:41:56,181 --> 00:41:58,266
I KNOW THAT VOICE.

822
00:41:58,391 --> 00:42:00,143
THAT FACE,
I KNOW IT.

823
00:42:00,268 --> 00:42:02,061
I SAW IT.

824
00:42:02,187 --> 00:42:03,813
HE MURDERED THEM.

825
00:42:03,938 --> 00:42:06,483
THY SOUL,

826
00:42:06,649 --> 00:42:09,235
FREEZE THY YOUNG BLOOD.

827
00:42:11,988 --> 00:42:14,240
IT'S AN ORDER.

828
00:42:14,366 --> 00:42:16,826
GIVE ME THE WEAPON.

829
00:42:16,951 --> 00:42:17,994
IF THOU DIDST EVER

830
00:42:18,119 --> 00:42:20,579
THY DEAR FATHER LOVE...

831
00:42:20,705 --> 00:42:22,499
GET BACK
TO THE SICK BAY.

832
00:42:22,623 --> 00:42:23,958
GO ON.

833
00:42:25,418 --> 00:42:27,504
[APPLAUSE]

834
00:42:35,345 --> 00:42:38,890
IT'S GOING BEAUTIFULLY.

835
00:42:39,015 --> 00:42:39,849
WHAT IS IT?

836
00:42:39,974 --> 00:42:41,393
WHAT'S WRONG?

837
00:42:41,518 --> 00:42:42,894
THERE WAS A VOICE
OUT OF THE PAST

838
00:42:43,019 --> 00:42:44,354
HAUNTING ME,

839
00:42:44,479 --> 00:42:45,730
TORTURING ME.

840
00:42:45,855 --> 00:42:48,649
THERE WAS ANOTHER PART
I ONCE PLAYED LONG AGO.

841
00:42:48,774 --> 00:42:49,484
I NEVER TOLD YOU
ABOUT IT.

842
00:42:49,608 --> 00:42:52,028
NOW THAT SAME CURTAIN
RISES AGAIN.

843
00:42:52,153 --> 00:42:52,862
THE TIME HAS COME.

844
00:42:52,987 --> 00:42:54,489
NO, FATHER.

845
00:42:54,613 --> 00:42:56,782
THE TIME
WILL NEVER COME.

846
00:42:56,908 --> 00:42:58,034
TONIGHT,

847
00:42:58,159 --> 00:43:00,245
AFTER MY PERFORMANCE,

848
00:43:00,370 --> 00:43:02,330
THE LAST TWO
WHO CAN HARM YOU

849
00:43:02,455 --> 00:43:05,417
WILL BE GONE.

850
00:43:05,542 --> 00:43:06,959
WHAT ARE YOU SAYING?

851
00:43:07,085 --> 00:43:08,461
THERE WERE 9.

852
00:43:08,586 --> 00:43:10,171
NOW THERE ARE ONLY TWO,

853
00:43:10,296 --> 00:43:12,549
AND THEY WILL BE GONE
AS SOON AS I.

854
00:43:18,012 --> 00:43:20,515
DON'T LOOK AT ME
LIKE THAT.

855
00:43:20,639 --> 00:43:22,641
WHAT HAVE YOU DONE?

856
00:43:22,767 --> 00:43:24,643
WHAT HAD TO BE DONE.

857
00:43:24,769 --> 00:43:26,479
THEY HAD TO BE
SILENCED.

858
00:43:27,063 --> 00:43:28,565
ALL OF THEM?

859
00:43:28,689 --> 00:43:30,442
ALL 7?

860
00:43:30,567 --> 00:43:31,859
MORE BLOOD
ON MY HANDS?

861
00:43:31,984 --> 00:43:34,237
NO, FATHER.
NOT ANYMORE.

862
00:43:34,362 --> 00:43:35,905
I'M STRONG, FATHER.

863
00:43:36,030 --> 00:43:37,156
IT'S NOTHING.

864
00:43:37,282 --> 00:43:39,033
Stagehand:
SECOND ACT--
3 MINUTES.

865
00:43:39,158 --> 00:43:40,826
WE'LL BE READY.

866
00:43:40,952 --> 00:43:42,745
DON'T YOU SEE?

867
00:43:42,870 --> 00:43:44,663
ALL THE GHOSTS ARE DEAD.

868
00:43:45,164 --> 00:43:46,624
I'VE BURIED THEM.

869
00:43:48,960 --> 00:43:52,004
THERE'S NO MORE BLOOD
ON YOUR HANDS.

870
00:43:52,130 --> 00:43:53,047
OH, MY CHILD.

871
00:43:53,172 --> 00:43:55,425
MY CHILD.

872
00:43:55,550 --> 00:43:57,760
YOU'VE LEFT ME
NOTHING!

873
00:44:01,473 --> 00:44:03,808
YOU WERE THE ONE THING
IN MY LIFE

874
00:44:03,933 --> 00:44:06,561
UNTOUCHED
BY WHAT I'D DONE.

875
00:44:06,685 --> 00:44:08,480
BUT YOU'RE SAFE NOW,
FATHER.

876
00:44:09,730 --> 00:44:11,149
I'VE SAVED YOU.

877
00:44:13,025 --> 00:44:14,777
NOW...

878
00:44:14,902 --> 00:44:16,946
NO ONE CAN TOUCH YOU.

879
00:44:20,325 --> 00:44:22,619
NOT EVEN CAPTAIN KIRK.

880
00:44:26,164 --> 00:44:28,541
SEE CAESAR COME.

881
00:44:32,837 --> 00:44:34,547
HE'S AWED
BY YOUR GREATNESS...

882
00:44:40,553 --> 00:44:42,472
YOUR SHINING
BRIGHTNESS.

883
00:44:46,267 --> 00:44:49,437
BRIGHT AS A BLADE...

884
00:44:49,562 --> 00:44:51,981
BEFORE IT IS
STAINED WITH BLOOD.

885
00:44:53,107 --> 00:44:56,110
BRIGHT AS A BLADE.

886
00:44:56,235 --> 00:44:57,195
COME WITH ME,

887
00:44:57,320 --> 00:44:57,903
BOTH OF YOU.

888
00:44:58,029 --> 00:45:00,156
OF COURSE.

889
00:45:00,281 --> 00:45:01,698
AFTER THE PLAY.

890
00:45:01,824 --> 00:45:03,326
THE PLAY IS OVER.

891
00:45:03,451 --> 00:45:05,036
IT'S BEEN OVER
FOR 20 YEARS.

892
00:45:05,161 --> 00:45:07,330
I WAS A SOLDIER
IN A CAUSE.

893
00:45:07,455 --> 00:45:09,332
THERE WERE THINGS
TO BE DONE.
TERRIBLE THINGS.

894
00:45:09,457 --> 00:45:10,375
STOP IT, FATHER!

895
00:45:10,500 --> 00:45:13,127
YOU HAVE NOTHING
TO JUSTIFY.

896
00:45:13,252 --> 00:45:15,463
MURDER, FLIGHT,

897
00:45:15,588 --> 00:45:18,841
SUICIDE, MADNESS.

898
00:45:18,966 --> 00:45:21,010
I NEVER WANTED
THE BLOOD ON MY HANDS

899
00:45:21,135 --> 00:45:22,679
EVER TO STAIN YOU.

900
00:45:22,803 --> 00:45:23,971
I DID IT FOR YOU.

901
00:45:24,096 --> 00:45:25,306
I'VE SAVED YOU.

902
00:45:25,431 --> 00:45:27,141
BY KILLING
7 INNOCENT MEN.

903
00:45:27,266 --> 00:45:29,435
THEY WEREN'T INNOCENT!

904
00:45:29,561 --> 00:45:31,604
THEY WERE DANGEROUS!

905
00:45:31,728 --> 00:45:32,605
I WOULD HAVE
KILLED A WORLD

906
00:45:32,729 --> 00:45:33,648
TO SAVE HIM!

907
00:45:33,772 --> 00:45:36,150
Stagehand:
CURTAIN GOING UP--
ONE MINUTE.

908
00:45:38,777 --> 00:45:39,987
THE PLAY, CAPTAIN.

909
00:45:40,112 --> 00:45:41,822
HE MUST GO ON.

910
00:45:44,659 --> 00:45:45,910
THIS IS THE GREAT...

911
00:45:46,035 --> 00:45:47,828
KARIDIAN.

912
00:45:47,953 --> 00:45:49,372
GUARD.

913
00:45:49,497 --> 00:45:52,375
YOU CANNOT DENY HIM
HIS LAST PERFORMANCE!

914
00:45:55,086 --> 00:45:56,504
LENORE, DON'T!

915
00:45:56,629 --> 00:45:58,297
AAH!
AAH!

916
00:46:00,841 --> 00:46:02,885
YOU'LL NEVER
GET OFF THE SHIP.

917
00:46:03,010 --> 00:46:06,389
THEN IT WILL BECOME
FLOATING, TOO,

918
00:46:06,514 --> 00:46:09,183
DRIFTING THROUGH SPACE

919
00:46:09,308 --> 00:46:11,519
WITH THE SOUL
OF THE GREAT KARIDIAN

920
00:46:11,644 --> 00:46:12,937
GIVING PERFORMANCES

921
00:46:13,062 --> 00:46:15,273
AT EVERY STAR HE TOUCHES.

922
00:46:21,362 --> 00:46:23,448
I KNOW HOW
TO USE THIS, CAPTAIN.

923
00:46:24,907 --> 00:46:25,908
NO.

924
00:46:26,033 --> 00:46:27,826
CAESAR,

925
00:46:27,952 --> 00:46:30,246
BEWARE THE IDES OF MARCH.

926
00:46:30,371 --> 00:46:31,623
NO, CHILD! DON'T!

927
00:46:31,748 --> 00:46:32,624
UHH!

928
00:46:34,875 --> 00:46:37,420
AAH!

929
00:46:42,383 --> 00:46:43,468
FATHER.

930
00:46:46,638 --> 00:46:48,389
FATHER.

931
00:46:50,057 --> 00:46:51,768
O...

932
00:46:51,892 --> 00:46:52,809
PROUD...

933
00:46:52,935 --> 00:46:53,645
DEATH!

934
00:46:55,271 --> 00:46:57,022
WHAT FEAST IS TOWARD

935
00:46:57,148 --> 00:46:59,525
IN THINE ETERNAL CELL...

936
00:47:00,735 --> 00:47:04,113
THAT THOU,
SUCH A PRINCE,

937
00:47:04,238 --> 00:47:06,532
AT A SHOT SO BLOODILY

938
00:47:06,658 --> 00:47:08,534
HAST STRUCK?

939
00:47:08,660 --> 00:47:10,995
[SOBBING]

940
00:47:14,332 --> 00:47:16,626
THE CURT--
THE CURTAIN.

941
00:47:16,751 --> 00:47:19,003
THE CURTAIN RISES.

942
00:47:21,964 --> 00:47:23,716
IT RISES.

943
00:47:26,135 --> 00:47:28,680
'TIS NO TIME TO SLEEP.

944
00:47:31,265 --> 00:47:32,933
THE PLAY.

945
00:47:33,976 --> 00:47:35,645
THE PLAY.

946
00:47:37,313 --> 00:47:40,274
THE PLAY'S THE THING...

947
00:47:42,109 --> 00:47:46,405
WHEREIN WE'LL CATCH
THE CONSCIENCE OF THE KING.

948
00:48:20,064 --> 00:48:20,815
MEDICAL REPORT.

949
00:48:20,939 --> 00:48:22,650
[BEEP]

950
00:48:25,069 --> 00:48:26,111
SHE'LL RECEIVE
THE BEST OF CARE, JIM.

951
00:48:26,237 --> 00:48:27,613
SHE REMEMBERS NOTHING.

952
00:48:27,739 --> 00:48:29,866
SHE EVEN THINKS
HER FATHER'S STILL ALIVE

953
00:48:29,990 --> 00:48:32,410
GIVING PERFORMANCES
BEFORE CHEERING CROWDS.

954
00:48:36,080 --> 00:48:38,249
YOU REALLY
CARED FOR HER,
DIDN'T YOU?

955
00:48:38,374 --> 00:48:40,917
READY TO LEAVE
BENECIA ORBIT,
CAPTAIN.

956
00:48:41,043 --> 00:48:43,254
STAND BY,
MR. LESLIE.

957
00:48:43,379 --> 00:48:45,130
ALL CHANNELS CLEARED,
UHURA?

958
00:48:45,256 --> 00:48:47,132
ALL CHANNELS CLEAR, SIR.

959
00:48:47,258 --> 00:48:48,551
WHENEVER YOU'RE READY,
MR. LESLIE.

960
00:48:48,676 --> 00:48:51,679
LEAVING ORBIT,
SIR.

961
00:48:51,804 --> 00:48:54,014
YOU'RE NOT GOING TO
ANSWER MY QUESTION,
ARE YOU?

962
00:48:57,643 --> 00:48:59,936
AHEAD WARP FACTOR 1,
MR. LESLIE.

963
00:49:04,275 --> 00:49:05,610
THAT'S AN ANSWER.
